Python Crash Course ==> project 1: Alien Invasion

# Hierachy
alien_invasion.py	: initialization, entrance file to run this game by calling 'run()' function
game_function.py	: define elements(ship, bullets, aliens) operation functions
alien.py			: Alien class definition
bullet.py			: Bullet class definition
ship.py				: Ship class definition
button.py			: Button class definition, mainly for 'Play' button right now
game_stats.py		: Stat class definiton, recording ship_limit, scores and high_score
scoreboard.py		: ScoreBoard class definition, displaying instant score while playing
setting.py			: Setting class definition, configuring elements properties
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
